data.description: ***Price Improvement***.  MOTIVATED SELLER!  Beautifully updated and move in ready!  An extra wide stair case greets you as walk into this beautiful split entry floor plan.  This home boasts a spacious living room with vaulted ceilings and a fireplace.  Next you will discover a beautiful kitchen with granite countertops, a double oven, and a pantry!  The dining room walks out to a deck and a lower patio.  Enjoy a fenced yard, perfect for kids and pets!  The master suite has a walk in closet and oversized vanity.  The laundry room is on the main floor in the main bathroom.   Un-finished basement is a blank canvas ready for your personal touch.  Recent updates include a newer roof, hard wood floors, shutters, and exterior paint.  Buyer and buyers agent to confirm all details.
